{"word":"καίω","slug":"καίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαίω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ orig.\">orig.</a> obscure] ‘cause to be on fire’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on providing illumination <b>light, kindle <a href='B:470 5:15'>Mt 5:15</a>; <a href='B:730 4:5'>Rv 4:5</a>;</b> in imagery <b><a href='B:490 12:35'>Lk 12:35</a>; <a href='B:500 5:35'>J 5:35</a>; <a href='B:730 8:10'>Rv 8:10</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on flaming or consumptive aspect <b><a href='B:500 15:6'>J 15:6</a>; <a href='B:530 13:3'>1 Cor 13:3</a>; <a href='B:650 12:18'>Hb 12:18</a>; <a href='B:730 8:8'>Rv 8:8</a>; <a href='B:730 19:20'>19:20</a>; <a href='B:730 21:8'>21:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in extended sense of emotional experience <b><a href='B:490 24:32'>Lk 24:32</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καίτοιγε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κἀκεῖ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}